As well it is.

295
00:18:30,629 --> 00:18:31,896
See these marks?

296
00:18:33,666 --> 00:18:35,500
Thracians notch their hilts.

297
00:18:35,500 --> 00:18:36,968
One for every kill.

298
00:18:39,305 --> 00:18:42,173
<i>How many made to yours after
