the magistrate's son?

317
00:19:40,099 --> 00:19:42,066
Apologies,
if I offered out of turn.

318
00:19:42,066 --> 00:19:44,335
Fuck apologies!

319
00:19:44,335 --> 00:19:45,904
Shrewd maneuvering,
if ever I saw it!

320
00:19:46,939 --> 00:19:48,173
I'll make a roman of you yet!

